# Attacks small businesses  can be exposed to
1. Monetary theft
2. Spam
3. Credential attack
4. Cross-site request Forgery (csrf)

# Measures to mitigate attacks
1. Use Strong Password with a minimum of 12 characters
2. limit Access And Privilege of users
3. Apply Defense in-depth such as 2-factor authentication 
4. Sanitize the Data
5. Keep Code Private

